          "id": "f_bb20000001",
          "title": "7 chars at base62 = 3.5T addressable codes",
          "body": "Even at 1M new links per day we wouldn't hit collision cliff for centuries. 6 chars (56B) felt borderline; bumped to 7 for headroom.",
